{"tid":2117993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連特朗普承認自己唔戴口罩係做錯 咁一眾熱青城、白票兵fans又如何面對？","createTime":"2020-07-21T07:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T23:50:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":31,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"4977378c2dafe6a9f1103176782c62d4dff655e5","tid":2117993,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻縮入去老母個臭西度"},{"pid":"91f800edea911c2a076feb010e56f7ba68084c6e","tid":2117993,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2527102/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2527102%2F&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=85c3f05e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2527102/</a>"},{"pid":"6862fe6cbb066e843c16c9ec1ea0ed550d19ceeb","tid":2117993,"uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"【改稱「戴口罩是好事」】特朗普認衰：人人都會犯錯 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3jqL0sQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3jqL0sQ&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=343a4e0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3jqL0sQ</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統 #特朗普 民意落後，上周更換競選經理「變陣」，加上美國新冠肺炎疫情持續失控，他終於不再「死牛一面頸」，繼捨棄大型造勢大會、首次舉行「電話集會」（telephonic rallies）後，在霍士新聞周日專訪中亦終承認抗疫上有些犯錯，並認為 #戴口罩 是好事。<br />\n<br />\n對於外界質疑美國抗疫缺乏「國家計劃」，特朗普終於承認「人人都會犯錯」。曾反對戴口罩的特朗普更放軟口風，說戴口罩是好事，強調他反對頒布全國口罩令只因希望國民擁有一定程度的自由。他更指摘白宮首席傳染病專家福西（Anthony Fauci）一邊危言聳聽，一邊錯誤地反對暫停中美往來航班，幸好他沒有聽從；但他重申與福西關係良好。<br />\n<br />\n然而，他在專訪中再次淡化疫情，揚言美國確診人數上升僅因讓全球羨慕的檢測數目，並重申美國是死亡率最低的國家之一。他又不忘聲討民主黨總統候選人、前副總統 #拜登，批評對方「無厘神氣」兼治國無能，甚至「不知道自己還活着」，質疑拜登能否通過認知能力測試。特朗普揚言，一旦拜登當選將摧毀國家，勢必下令削減警察經費、稅收增加3倍、宗教將在美國消失。<br />\n<br />\n對於在民調大幅落後，特朗普狠批是虛假民調，白宮民調顯示他正領先。根據美國國廣播公司（ABC）與《華盛頓郵報》最新民調，拜登全國支持率拋離特朗普15個百分點。惟霍士最新調查顯示，拜登支持率49%，僅領先特朗普8個百分點，優勢較6月收窄。"},{"pid":"400507a7125c54d88d030f0d77bb863b26894ea6","tid":2117993,"uid":9747,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"熱共唔敢入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一票不投熱共"},{"pid":"f8247c2ef3cdfe901ddd8c49a992e0a7cb8964ce","tid":2117993,"uid":34771,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"熱狗：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;(hang撚左機)"},{"pid":"923d37e8d0f772968229bc686aa133749ba544c6","tid":2117993,"uid":185656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"Trump自甘墮落,老師唔會再牧養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7e97734d36ec186d0008af104cc5ad303359c1","tid":2117993,"uid":81698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:16:57.000Z","msg":"今次老朋友不給面子了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa32f3e871a90a61055c086c34167a2938df8d0","tid":2117993,"uid":50931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"923d37e8d0f772968229bc686aa133749ba544c6","tid":2117993,"uid":185656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"Trump自甘墮落,老師唔會再牧養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/f